  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL35">
<l>tāviyaṉ ṟulaka mellām talaiviḷāk koṇṭa ventāy</l>
<l>cēviyē ṉuṉṉai yallāṟ cikkeṉac ceṅkaṇ mālē</l>
<l>āviyē yamutē yeṉṟaṉā ruyi raṉaiya ventāy</l>
<l>pāviyē ṉuṉṉai yallāṟ pāviyēṉ pāvi yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Father who crossed the whole world that day [and]</l>
<l rend="indent">spread over [everyone’s] heads!</l>
<l>O red-eyed Māl! I shall definitely not worship anyone but You!</l>
<l>O my Life-breath! O Nectar! O my Father akin to precious life!</l>
<l>I, a sinner, shall not meditate on [anyone] but You,</l>
<l rend="indent">I, a sinner.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
